{"tid":811511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"十年一別！潮流教母徐濠縈潮店結業","createTime":"2018-09-09T01:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T03:56:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d95929a85e904db00bf75202fb6ee98916c47c3","tid":811511,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/093211_330783f3790992c72bfefb0a7bfe213c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F093211_330783f3790992c72bfefb0a7bfe213c.png&h=8807dfbb&s={SIZE}\" />身為「時裝精」的天王陳奕迅太太徐濠縈，十年前在香港成立時尚生活概念店Liger，為本地潮界注入新力量及推動時裝文化，多年來引入不少小眾但設計獨特的品牌，並常推出不少聯乘合作。惟Liger宣布要「十年一別」，於下月（十月）正式結業並將會搞告別派對。身為徐濠縈經理人的鄭紹康，接受東網查詢時，被問到Liger結業原因，他說一切留待徐濠縈在派對上解說。<br />\n<br />\nLiger的官方Instagram發表告別感言，表示感激十年來顧客、媒體及時裝品牌的支持，尤其顧客長年的關愛，令她們感動莫名：「我們很慶幸當初開始了 Liger；十年來的點滴，那麼多的重要時刻，加上種種轉折不同的經歷，我倆也無法忘記。希望大家繼續發揮香港女性的獨立精神，一直當個最愛時裝的、獨一無異的Liger Woman。Liger 的結束並沒帶著（着）遺憾，只可說既然這段旅程來到了終點，倒不如讓我們稍作休息，再尋找下一個目標繼續努力！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180908/mobile/bkn-20180908232844330-0908_00862_001.html?conversationContext=1&amp;conversationContext=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180908%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180908232844330-0908_00862_001.html%3FconversationContext%3D1%26conversationContext%3D1&d=Zdays%2Fva7Gj8FXNPFS381cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f4a66bc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180908/mobile/bkn-20180908232844330-0908_00862_001.html?conversationContext=1&amp;conversationContext=1</a>"},{"pid":"eaac3b01a9c7c0f3d39079cd37a337a0de0d23de","tid":811511,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"成千上萬個門口<br />\n總有一個人要先走"},{"pid":"3b1c847ee936a3089d500195b63d3e7f007998b7","tid":811511,"uid":82917,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyT